00:36:45.769 --> 00:36:51.852
Now on the right side, the yellow coloured line, you see,

00:36:52.018 --> 00:36:56.644
ends up into another yellow coloured institution,

00:36:56.852 --> 00:37:02.976
is a result or a by-product of our activity,

00:37:03.435 --> 00:37:09.602
physical and through our brain, which we call as mental.

00:37:09.852 --> 00:37:14.060
This creates an institution called ego.

00:37:14.393 --> 00:37:18.101
So we have got superego as well as ego.

00:37:18.352 --> 00:37:21.226
Supposing you tell somebody, "Don't do like this.

00:37:21.435 --> 00:37:24.935
