00:37:25.185 --> 00:37:27.226
Then, if you go too much with it,

00:37:27.435 --> 00:37:29.644
then conditioning takes place in a person.

00:37:29.852 --> 00:37:34.976
And these conditionings are expressed as a balloon there,

00:37:35.435 --> 00:37:38.518
which is a by-product of conditionings.

00:37:38.852 --> 00:37:43.435
And the another one is the by-product of our activity,

00:37:43.894 --> 00:37:47.143
which is mental as well as physical.

00:37:47.435 --> 00:37:52.852
So we have two things, one is the manasa, is mana.

00:37:53.060 --> 00:37:56.644
I don't know, in English it is called as mind,

00:37:56.852 --> 00:38:02.101
but it is confusion, because they call a mental case to a mad man and

00:38:02.352 --> 00:38:05.894
when you work through your brain, you call it a mental activity.

