00:38:11.518 --> 00:38:13.644
has to be understood properly.

00:38:13.852 --> 00:38:18.810
What happens to a man who works through his brain too much,

00:38:19.060 --> 00:38:20.560
gets a heart attack.

00:38:20.769 --> 00:38:23.976
It's surprising, he should get something wrong there -

00:38:24.185 --> 00:38:26.185
but no, he gets a heart attack.

00:38:26.393 --> 00:38:30.644
A man, who works for the future through his mental capacity,

00:38:30.852 --> 00:38:33.310
gets a heart attack, means a balance.

00:38:33.518 --> 00:38:38.685
And then a man, who works with his emotions too much,

00:38:38.935 --> 00:38:44.393
gets this brain which is degenerated, so you call it mental.

00:38:44.602 --> 00:38:48.769
So because of this the confusion is there, because of the balance.

00:38:48.935 --> 00:38:51.268
It's surprising, that in a mental hospital

00:38:51.518 --> 00:38:55.185
you don't need anything to find out about heart,

00:38:55.393 --> 00:38:57.393
electrocardiogram and all that is not needed,

00:38:57.602 --> 00:39:01.143
because a mental case never gets a heart attack normally.

00:39:01.435 --> 00:39:04.477
